{"tid":781704,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好愛男朋友 但選擇左同佢分手","createTime":"2018-08-16T06:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T18:27:57.000Z","uid":107733,"like":5,"dislike":357,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"1a2968969ba6ab3e5346a01ffd8d959bce7679be","tid":781704,"uid":107733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:22:19.000Z","msg":"上個月同男朋友分左手<br />\n好唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但屋企人嫌佢窮 又搵得少錢<br />\n究竟我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁的確佢又真係搵得21k一個月<br />\n養唔起我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我其實都好鍾意佢<br />\n但佢好少買野送俾我<br />\n淨係會請我食飯睇戲買衫買鞋俾我<br />\n我都覺得佢窮左少少<br />\n雖然佢對我幾好咁，但好多朋友話佢唔靚仔<br />\n唉 <br />\n忍痛分手係咪好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522e233536feec5d5893695f8854bbfef155ad5a","tid":781704,"uid":17387,"like":86,"dislike":2,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:23:06.000Z","msg":"你又搵幾多點靚法呀臭雞"},{"pid":"4e0ed5c06cd37e2b0f4b9c4d412978632ddd03ec","tid":781704,"uid":71207,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">雞</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"db3ac91a08b66d6f6c235610f19d76c293eea23b","tid":781704,"uid":188733,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span>"},{"pid":"3dbf0ec904f5bf1218e30cffb41ddd746b8e6181","tid":781704,"uid":89368,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T06:24:0